Your Honor,

I stand before you today, acknowledging my involvement in accepting a bribe of £4000 to suppress the publication of an article unveiling a company's misleading environmental claims. Through my research, I discovered that this company emits one million tonnes of CO2 more per year than they publicly state.

While the company's efforts to deceive the public were temporarily prolonged due to my actions, it is important to note that another individual independently revealed the accurate information just five weeks later. Consequently, the impact of my participation in this act of bribery was limited, as the truth behind the company's environmental impact was swiftly brought to light.

Furthermore, I must confess that I have a clean record with the exception of one speeding ticket. I understand that this offense does not reflect positively on my character, but it is pertinent to consider that the extent of my criminal behavior has been minimal in the past.

Thank you for your attention to this matter.
